data.description: Introducing the essence of lavish living - 250 Lake Dr, Lemoore, CA. Nestled within an esteemed gated community, this 4-bedroom 3 bath haven is a masterpiece of elegance, featuring recent stucco and paint upgrades, alongside meticulously remodeled bathrooms. Step into a realm of absolute luxury as you're welcomed by an expansive layout where the gourmet kitchen takes center stage. ensuring culinary delights are a daily affair. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of your surroundings as large windows unveil captivating views of the adjacent golf course, allowing you to bask in the natural beauty while maintaining your private haven. But the allure doesn't end indoors - the property presents an outdoor oasis complete with a sparkling pool and inviting spa, inviting you to unwind in style. This idyllic residence also enjoys easy access to schools and shopping enhancing your lifestyle at every corner. Luxury, comfort, and sophistication converge at 250 Lake Dr. This is your invitation to experience the extraordinary - schedule your private viewing today and seize the opportunity to call this remarkable property your forever home
